cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS

This paper discusses the architecture and security challenges of mobile edge computing in the context of IoT applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses security and privacy challenges, which suggests that cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another likely category. The paper also discusses efficiency challenges, which suggests that cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SE (Software Engineering) are also possible categories. Finally, the paper discusses data analysis, which suggests that cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible category.
